<plot>Columbia Pictures production number 9857. Film and radio stars are shown vacationing, golfing and attending style shows, showing the latest fashions in "new-look" bathing suits, at California's Arrowhead Springs Resort. Some are. Others are shown in stock footage from earlier Screen Snapshots shorts. Those shown include 'Andy Clyde' (qv), 'Jerry Colonna' (qv), 'Barbara Jo Allen' (qv) as Vera Vague, 'Ann Richards (I)' (qv), 'Cathy Carter (I)' (qv) and'Paulette Goddard' (qv).</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?482192</url></doc>
